"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">想大個仔獨立必睇</span></span></span></strong><br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><ins>香港人一定要知！</ins></strong></span></span>遇怪魔想變大個，就一定一定要睇！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span></span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"674221a729f7610d2517e0409a5811a2648c9f80","tid":1535081,"uid":191271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"38d0ac798f3ae5a049c73ee5cafeb2ac14b7046a","tid":1535081,"uid":119478,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:32:39.000Z","msg":"答案係乜<br />\n我相信好多香港人心中一早有答案<br />\n只係唔敢講個四個字出黎<br />\n甚至唔敢諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:33:17.000Z","msg":"一步步黎<br />\n<br />\n下步就係廢左張聲明"},{"pid":"b352540ce0354529eb11bb440d6d774c8da94c77","tid":1535081,"uid":59465,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:33:18.000Z","msg":"我都覺得訴求依兩個字唔好<br />\n好似低佢哋一等咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大命令就差唔多"},{"pid":"af32b1b86c8c58591c2037ab39c9fb58057f14bd","tid":1535081,"uid":191271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b352540ce0354529eb11bb440d6d774c8da94c77","tid":1535081,"u